title: 2012 Audi a3 2.0T Premium Wagon 4D
car_description_text:
Selling my beloved 2012 A3 2.0T with manual transmission, non-quattro.   

- Regular & frequent oil changes
- Great HVAC (regularly replaced cabin filters)
- Black leather interior, heated seats (everything in great condition)
- Dual glass, panoramic moonroof
- Radiator was replaced  200 miles ago, with OEM parts due to a bad sensor (CA carb compliance part). 
- At around 100k miles I had the serpentine belt, radiator, and thermostat replaced.  
- No accidents

I've owned the car since 2012, bought it used from the dealership at Auto Gallery here in Los Angeles, as a lease return.  The car has been extremely reliable in the 12 years of ownership. 

Selling since I drive the car way less now that I picked up the Bronco, which fits my lifestyle more. 

Sorry for the repost, - somehow Facebook mistook the first listening as trademark infringement. See less
